title: 10 breakout players, 49ers offseason grade (Football 05/22)
description:
Pete Prisco joins Will Brinson to talk about his breakout players list and to break down whether or not the 49ers prepared themselves to win 10 games with their offseason moves. The guys also discuss the only great place to host a Super Bowl (New Orleans) and run through the rest of the NFL news.
